      "code": "1.",
      "name": "EXCEPT THOSE NOTED, ALL PUBLIC AREAS HAVE NO CEILING. {\\fMicrosoft YaHei|b0|i0|c134|p34;DESIGN DESCRIPTION } 除有注释的顶面外,其它均无吊顶。 2. THE POSITION OF INSPECTION WHOLE SHOULD BE FIXED PER ON-SITE ARCHITECT'S SUGGESTION. 石膏板吊顶面检修口。须根据现场实际情况在建筑师的建议下准确定位。 {\\fMicrosoft YaHei|b0|i0|c134|p34;设计说明} CODE 代码 SPECIFICATION 说明 喷淋 SPRINKLER 烟雾探测器 SMOKE SENSOR 消防喇叭 CODE 代码 SPECIFICATION 说明 NETWORK AP (ALL AP POINTS MOVED TO THE SOUTHEAST CORNER OF THE SERVER ROOM. 网络AP (所有 AP点位拉至东南角机房。 交换机和机柜由施工方深化) CAMERA (CAMERA CONNECTED TO THE PARK'S MAIN SYSTEM) 摄像头 (摄像头连接园区大系统) CODE 代码 LF3 LF3a LF3b 嵌入式可调角射灯 LED 9W /24度 /2700K{\\fArial|b0|i0|c0|p34; ADJUSTABLE DOWNLIGHT} 嵌入式可调角射灯 LED 7W /24度 /2700K{\\fArial|b0|i0|c0|p34; ADJUSTABLE DOWNLIGHT} 嵌入式可调角射灯 LED 7W /36度 /2700K{\\fArial|b0|i0|c0|p34; ADJUSTABLE DOWNLIGHT} SPECIFICATION 说明"
